title: Stone Wall PBR Materials Vol 3.1
description: PBR material with high resolution (4096x4096): Stone Wall materials consisting of 24 units.
longDescription: For each material there is a texture of the base color, a normal map, a mask with roughness, height map, and ambient occlusion.
technicalDetails:
Features:

  • PBR Materials

Texture Size: (4096x4096)

Texture Resolutions:

  • The number of texture base colors (bump is in the alpha channel): 24
  • The number of normal maps: 24
  • The number of masks (roughness, height map, ambient occlusion): 24
  • The number of macro version: 1 (1024x1024)

Number of Master Material (texture size 4096x4096): 8

Number of Materials (texture size 4096x4096): 24

Number of Master Material (texture size 2048x2048) 8

Number of Materials (texture size 2048x2048): 24

Do Materials derive from a Master Material with instances as variation: Yes

Number of Textures: 72 (4096x4096), 72 (2048x2048), 1 (1024x1024)

Supported Development Platforms: (Windows, Mac, PS4, IOS, Android, Xbox One, Oculus)

Supported Target Build Platforms: (Windows, Mac, PS4, IOS, Android, Xbox One, Oculus)
